OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and bright to
OL,6,Fstart. Cloud will thicken through the
OL,7,Fday to give the odd spot of rain at
OL,8,Ftimes. Gentle east to southeast
OL,9,Fbreezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA rather cloudy evening with
OL,12,Fsome patchy light rain possible at
OL,13,Ftimes. Remaining mainly cloudy through
OL,14,Fthe rest of the night with a few mist
OL,15,For fog patches developing.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FBright but with few spots of
OL,18,Flight rain not to be ruled out, though
OL,19,Fmany places staying dry until
OL,20,Foutbreaks of rain spread across from
OL,21,Fthe southwest by late afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
